<inglise> Natural or legal persons or groups of such persons who harvest grapes, hereinafter referred to as 'harvesters', shall submit each year to the competent authorities designated by the Member States a harvest declaration in the administrative unit specified, containing at least the information specified in Table A of Annex I and, where appropriate, Table Aa of Annex I. </inglise>
