<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The yield per hectare to be entered in the declarations referred to in Article 1 shall be determined by making the relation, for each of the categories of vineyard contained in Table A of Annex I, between the total quantity of grapes harvested and the area referred to in paragraph 1 from which they were obtained. </inglise>
